{"tid":32781,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「圖片分享」華山長空棧道","createTime":"2016-12-10T11:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T04:54:13.000Z","uid":37661,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c66fd3bc3de11346832e4b6a17dbbc786bb22bf5","tid":32781,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:36:53.000Z","msg":"分享幾年前去既長空棧道。<br />\n<br />\n長空棧道，如果你唔敢落去，在上面會首先見到呢個石柱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030141_zpsjjzdji5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030141_zpsjjzdji5n.jpg&h=7a3645cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030146_zps2pqrdbgb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030146_zps2pqrdbgb.jpg&h=cb9676eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長空棧道中間一段<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030150_zpsibfzcrok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030150_zpsibfzcrok.jpg&h=62a42989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030149_zpsszxvpsnw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030149_zpsszxvpsnw.jpg&h=dc1699d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長空棧道過佐危險既木板後，會去到一個平地，呢張相係果度影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030170_zps9uwogtxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030170_zps9uwogtxr.jpg&h=e03eb9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長空棧道盡頭的石洞，傳說係以前啲人修練用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030164_zpss2xb5ztj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030164_zpss2xb5ztj.jpg&h=7627d33e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48d9c4977e74c850efe7fc0d27e2700e2571ee6d","tid":32781,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:37:29.000Z","msg":"嚇死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畏高撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04196f2683ec57a60091a69c4a7ce76cd108a5f","tid":32781,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:39:53.000Z","msg":"正喎喂"},{"pid":"38aa6c02f44db678ca225adfd895b594bad63da1","tid":32781,"uid":59480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"玩命"},{"pid":"1b809e9bef390a76ba377ecfa57fa1e9373d3a11","tid":32781,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚇死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畏高撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都嚇得死？<br />\n<br />\n如果咁呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030175a_zpss8arqzy9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030175a_zpss8arqzy9.jpg&h=394ad8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f330/aibohk/Travellife/Xian/P1030160a_zpshsa6ry1i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi50.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff330%2Faibohk%2FTravellife%2FXian%2FP1030160a_zpshsa6ry1i.jpg&h=468acdaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9004d3660fdeec9193cc6004784